						               													<description>User Summary:&amp;#10;Polemos: Risorgimento is a free to download miniature ruleset supplement to Polemos: Franco-Prussian War covering the Italian Wars of unification.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Two sizes of games are presented. The Risorgimento Fratelli d'Italia focuses on smaller scale actions with corps sized forces. One base of miniatures is to represent an infantry battalion of approximately 500 soldiers. For players who prefer army scale games Risorgimento Feldzeugmeister is the other part of the game. In Feldzeugmeister one base of miniatures represent brigades, approximately 2500 soldiers in the case of infantry.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is available from Baccus6mm in the U.K.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
